>The 11th Ebola outbreak in the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC) is declared over nearly six months after the first cases were reported in Equateur Province<\/p>\n                                <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                            <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item-image-container\">\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/stories\/the-ebola-outbreak-in-the-democratic-republic-of-the-congo-drc-is-declared-over\/\">\n                                                                                <picture>\n                                                <source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/06\/2019-Ebola-Merck-along-with-international-agencies-DSC08425.jpeg?w=1024?resize=133,133\">\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1279px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/06\/2019-Ebola-Merck-along-with-international-agencies-DSC08425.jpeg?w=1024?resize=141,144\">\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/06\/2019-Ebola-Merck-along-with-international-agencies-DSC08425.jpeg?w=1024?resize=180,180\">\n                                                <img\n                                                    data-src=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/06\/2019-Ebola-Merck-along-with-international-agencies-DSC08425.jpeg?w=1024?resize=180,180\"\n                                                    alt=\"Article thumbnail\"\n                                                    class=\"lazyload\"\n                                                    loading=\"lazy\"\n                                                \/>\n                                            <\/picture>\n                                                                            <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item\">\n                        \n                            <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item-content-container\">\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/stories\/merck-scientists-probe-how-our-bodies-bugs-impact-immunity-and-disease\/\">\n                                                                        <small class=\"tagline\">Innovation<\/small>\n                                    <h4><span>Merck scientists probe how our bodies&#8217; bugs impact immunity and disease<\/span><\/h4>\n                                    <p>Our researchers are pioneering new ways to research and understand the biology of new diseases by looking inside the human gut<\/p>\n                                <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                            <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item-image-container\">\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/stories\/merck-scientists-probe-how-our-bodies-bugs-impact-immunity-and-disease\/\">\n                                                                                <picture>\n                                                <source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/10\/Scientists-RY-Preparing-slide-1450-1-HI.jpg?w=1024?resize=133,133\">\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1279px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/10\/Scientists-RY-Preparing-slide-1450-1-HI.jpg?w=1024?resize=141,144\">\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/10\/Scientists-RY-Preparing-slide-1450-1-HI.jpg?w=1024?resize=180,180\">\n                                                <img\n                                                    data-src=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/10\/Scientists-RY-Preparing-slide-1450-1-HI.jpg?w=1024?resize=180,180\"\n                                                    alt=\"Article thumbnail\"\n                                                    class=\"lazyload\"\n                                                    loading=\"lazy\"\n                                                \/>\n                                            <\/picture>\n                                                                            <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item\">\n                        \n                            <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item-content-container\">\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/stories\/how-you-can-help-slow-the-threat-of-antimicrobial-resistance\/\">\n                                                                        <small class=\"tagline\">Health awareness<\/small>\n                                    <h4><span>How you can help slow the threat of antimicrobial resistance<\/span><\/h4>\n                                    <p>The growing burden of AMR threatens the return to a world without effective antibiotics<\/p>\n                                <\/a>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                            <div class=\"mco-featured-stories-e1-content-item-image-container\">\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/stories\/how-you-can-help-slow-the-threat-of-antimicrobial-resistance\/\">\n                                                                                <picture>\n                            