nt\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/04\/Patients-People-GettyImages-1188426098-People-hugging-by-sea-HI_101_high.jpg?resize=696,425\" >\n                <source media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1279px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/04\/Patients-People-GettyImages-1188426098-People-hugging-by-sea-HI_101_high.jpg?resize=384,468\">\n                <source media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/04\/Patients-People-GettyImages-1188426098-People-hugging-by-sea-HI_101_high.jpg?resize=650,544\" >\n                <img\n                    data-src=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2020\/04\/Patients-People-GettyImages-1188426098-People-hugging-by-sea-HI_101_high.jpg?resize=650,544\"\n                    alt=\"Two people embracing on a mountain with view of ocean\"\n                    class=\"lazyload mco-image-parallax-zoom-out\"\n                    loading=\"lazy\"\n                \/>\n            <\/picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"mco-b5-content-block-content-section parallax-scroll\">\n\t\t\t\n\t        <h3>Our commitment to patients is unwavering<\/h3>\n\n\t        \t            <div class=\"mco-b5-content-block-description\"><p>As long as there are still patients in hospitals, doctors desperate to add years to the lives of their patients, and a world where treatments aren&#8217;t accessible to all, we will be here: fighting with all we have to deliver more, sooner.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t        \t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mco-b5-content-block-content-buttons-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"btn secondary\" href=\"https:\/\/www.merck.com\/patients\/\" title=\"Learn more\" target=\"\">Learn more<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mco-b5-content-block-modal popup\" style=\"display: none;\">\n\t<div class=\"popup-wrapper\">\n\t\t<div class=\"mco-b